{
  "stem": "10960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shall register also if any children remained so they're taken to a kindergarten in order the parents shall be able to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came over, and he told me this story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, well, we will go to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, and?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, and I will not go to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will not sign it, and I will not give up my child to-- I do not believe them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wish the people would not believe them!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before they walked through the [NON-ENGLISH], each and every one could find a place where to hide himself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we were in [NON-ENGLISH], I still didn't believe them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was thinking to myself, if they will come through the ghetto, and see whether I have a child, and I didn't return it through the-- to them, to a kindergarten-- what, all of a sudden they want good-- a kindergarten?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this is what I said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I decided to go to a-- to a goyish-- to a-- a non-Jewish section where I shall try to find someone who is willing to trust me, and I shall be able to trust them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I shall pay them later, and they shall take me to Mlynow, to my sister's house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this I felt that Mlynow-- first of all, it's my sister who lives there with her family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, maybe until they will be able to-- this is what everybody used to say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are killing, because they made the active-- first, because this is a large city, Rovno But if-- if Mlynow is a small one, so let me try-- try, I thought to myself.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm trying to convince myself that there won't happen what happened in Rovno.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
